title: Dead Presidents Vol I & II (Big Papi) Funk Soul Soundtrack 2
description:
Source: 1995 and 1996 Sound CD's + Fresh Cover Art Scans


Tags have been edited so both Vol I and Vol II show up under 1 Album in player view (Disc 1 and Disc2) even though these were two separate releases. Each album does contain the correct embedded album art (iTunes won't recognize the 2 arts but apps like Foobar will be true to the tags).

If you want to have these show up as 2 Albums, change Disc 1 title to Dead Presidents and Disc 2 title to Dead Presidents Vol II. Also change Disc tag to 1/1 for each volume. That will make it correct database tags.



Whew, now that tag talk is done, despite the movie being so-so this is one of the best collections of funk soul music available on CD's. If you like the genre this is a must-have. I hope you enjoy.

- Big Papi
